---

# Dynamic Block Rendering Rules

The template contains temporary build-time placeholders that must be replaced or removed before final output.

These are not allowed to remain in final HTML:

- `PREHEADER_TEXT`
- `VIDEO_THUMBNAIL`
- `VIDEO_LINK`
- `CHURCH_CENTER_LINK`
- `SERMON_TITLE`
- `SCRIPTURE_PASSAGE`
- `SCRIPTURE_BIBLE_URL`
- `SERMON_DESCRIPTION`
- `SUMMARY_TEXT`
- `SUMMARY_TEXT_BLOCK`
- `SCRIPTURE_LINK_BLOCK`
- `SCRIPTURE_QUICK_LINK_BLOCK`
- `KEY_POINTS_BLOCK`
- `RESOURCES_SECTION`
- `HIGHLIGHT_SECTION`
- `HIGHLIGHT_THUMBNAIL_BLOCK`
- `SOCIAL_SHARE_BUTTON_ROW`
- Any `{{...}}` placeholder
- Any all-caps placeholder token that was intended for build-time substitution

---

# Summary Text Block Rendering

If `SUMMARY_TEXT` exists, render:

```html
<p class="summary-theme" style="font-size:15px; color:#4a5568; line-height:24px; margin:0 0 24px 0; padding:0; font-style:italic;">"Escaped summary text"</p>
```

If no summary text exists, render nothing.

---

# Scripture Link Block Rendering

If `SCRIPTURE_PASSAGE` and `SCRIPTURE_BIBLE_URL` exist, render:

```html
<a href="SCRIPTURE_BIBLE_URL" target="_blank" class="scripture-link" style="display:inline-block; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:#00819e !important; letter-spacing:0.5px; border-bottom:2px solid #00819e; padding-bottom:1px; margin:0 0 24px 0; text-decoration:none !important;">
  📖 SCRIPTURE_PASSAGE — Read on Bible.com →
</a>
```

If scripture is not available, render nothing.

---

# Scripture Quick Link Block Rendering

If `SCRIPTURE_PASSAGE` and `SCRIPTURE_BIBLE_URL` exist, render:

```html
<div class="quick-link-row" style="border-left:3px solid #00819e; padding:10px 0 10px 16px; margin:0;">
  <a href="SCRIPTURE_BIBLE_URL" target="_blank" style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:#00819e !important; text-decoration:none;">
    Read SCRIPTURE_PASSAGE on Bible.com →
  </a>
  <p class="quick-link-desc" style="font-size:13px; color:#718096; margin:2px 0 0 0; padding:0;">Follow along with this week's passage</p>
</div>
```

If scripture is not available, render nothing.

---

# Key Points Block Rendering

If key points exist, render:

```html
<hr class="divider" style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0; margin:0 0 20px 0;">
<p class="key-points-header" style="font-size:13px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#718096; margin:0 0 12px 0; padding:0;">Key Points</p>
<div class="key-point-row" style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
  <span class="key-point-number" style="display:inline-block; width:28px; height:28px; background-color:#00819e; color:#ffffff; font-size:13px; font-weight:900; text-align:center; line-height:28px; border-radius:50%; margin-right:10px; vertical-align:middle;">1</span>
  <span class="key-point-text" style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:#1a202c; vertical-align:middle;">Actual key point text</span>
</div>
```

Repeat one `.key-point-row` for each key point.

If no key points exist, render nothing.

---

# Resources Section Rendering

If qualifying resources exist, render:

```html
<tr>
  <td class="resources-cell" style="background-color:#f7f8fa; padding:28px 32px;">
    <p class="section-label" style="font-size:13px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#00819e; margin:0 0 16px 0; padding:0;">🔎 Sermon Resources</p>
    <p style="font-size:13px; color:#718096; margin:0 0 16px 0; padding:0;">Click any image to download</p>

    RESOURCE_ROWS

  </td>
</tr>
```

If no qualifying resources exist, render nothing.

